p It is currently #{moment().tz('America/New_York').format('MM/DD/YYYY HH:mm')} (ET)
p Please select customer and timeframe

form(action='/', method='POST')
  p
    | Customer:
    input(type='text', name='customer', value=customer, placeholder='e.g. tiffany')
    |             From:
    input(type='datetime-local', name='from_time', value=from_time)
    |             To:
    input(type='datetime-local', name='to_time', value=to_time)
  input(type='submit', value='Submit')
